summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2799 for the improvement of Etruria Street, from Nickerson Street to a point one hundred eighty (180) feet west of Warren Avenue, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; all in the City of Seattle, by the construction of concrete walks, with all necessary cross walks, under Ordinance No. 33474, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
